cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CR

This paper deals with object detection and viewpoint estimation from visual data, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of prior distributions and parametric models is also relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and cryptography (cs.CR).
